<br>
*Grummus<br>
*Terris Thule<br>
*The 4 Ancient Dragons in Sleepers<br>
*AOW<br>
<br>
We will be doing some more flagging events like Grummus, Behemoth, and Aerin'Dar over the next couple weeks before we leave them behind for quite some time. . .There is only so much fun any group should have to endure.<br>
<br>
